1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 13=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
("I like you."
The Crown Prince Confesses!)

4
00:00:53,390 --> 00:00:55,640
What are your orders, Your Highness?

5
00:01:09,930 --> 00:01:13,320
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

6
00:01:14,080 --> 00:01:17,460
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

7
00:01:18,950 --> 00:01:21,070
The Crown Prince
personally draped the cloak over her.

8
00:01:21,070 --> 00:01:22,430
I'm so jealous!

9
00:01:22,430 --> 00:01:23,870
Yeah, me too!

10
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,040
Thank you, Your Highness.

11
00:01:28,150 --> 00:01:29,280
But I'm really not cold.

12
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:32,980
The weather is freezing.

13
00:01:33,700 --> 00:01:34,940
Don't force yourself, Mrs. Pan.

14
00:01:34,960 --> 00:01:36,880
♪Though fate tries♪

15
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:39,460
♪To make us pass each other by♪

16
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:43,100
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

17
00:01:43,430 --> 00:01:44,430
This is pear soup.

18
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:45,410
Drink it while it's hot.

19
00:01:46,510 --> 00:01:48,200
(What is he trying to do?)

20
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:56,120
(Why is the Crown Prince
being so attentive to Li Qingqing?)

21
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:59,510
(A wolf in sheep's clothing.)

22
00:01:59,870 --> 00:02:01,350
(The soup must be poisoned.)

23
00:02:02,430 --> 00:02:03,400
My dear,

24
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:07,000
don't you think His Highness
is being a little too good to Qingqing?

25
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:09,590
Who does she think she is?

26
00:02:10,310 --> 00:02:12,680
His Highness is only
giving her special treatment

27
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,280
for my sake.

28
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:17,680
Li Qingqing,

29
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,430
I hope you realize

30
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,520
that you're only basking in my glory

31
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:26,080
for the Crown Prince
to treat you this well.

32
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,870
Once the banquet is over,

33
00:02:27,900 --> 00:02:30,430
remember to kneel and thank
His Highness properly for his grace.

34
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:33,030
Don't let others say
I don't know how to teach my wife.

35
00:02:38,880 --> 00:02:40,870
You've worked hard
these past few days, my dear.

36
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:41,800
Here,

37
00:02:42,590 --> 00:02:44,240
you can have this pear soup.

38
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,310
You know your place today.

39
00:02:47,310 --> 00:02:48,800
Well then,

40
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:51,030
just for tonight,

41
00:02:51,310 --> 00:02:52,960
I will gracefully...

42
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:53,700
Drink up, my dear.

43
00:02:57,150 --> 00:02:58,000
(Drink and die.)

44
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:58,910
Yang...

45
00:03:00,700 --> 00:03:01,430
You foolish woman!

46
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:03,230
Are you trying to choke me to death?

47
00:03:03,750 --> 00:03:04,470
Insolent!

48
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:19,030
Take Miss Qingqing
down to change her clothes first.

49
00:03:19,300 --> 00:03:20,080
Yes, Your Highness.

50
00:03:30,630 --> 00:03:31,400
Your Highness...

51
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:37,150
This is the changing area
for female guests.

52
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,080
Your Highness,

53
00:03:42,290 --> 00:03:44,120
it's inappropriate for you to enter,
don't you think?

54
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:47,360
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

55
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,710
Pan Yang is incompetent.

56
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,360
He doesn't deserve you at all.

57
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:54,800
Just how much longer

58
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,660
do you intend to stay
with a husband like him?

59
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:59,590
(Testing me again and again?)

60
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:01,870
No...

61
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:03,750
My husband treats me wonderfully.

62
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,710
It was my own clumsiness just now

63
00:04:05,710 --> 00:04:07,310
that made him angry.

64
00:04:07,470 --> 00:04:09,430
We share a deep affection
for each other.

65
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,870
I've never thought about divorce,

66
00:04:11,870 --> 00:04:13,080
and we will never separate.

67
00:04:13,630 --> 00:04:16,270
If you're only holding back
because of the Pan family, I can...

68
00:04:16,270 --> 00:04:16,850
Your Highness,

69
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,360
I

70
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:20,000
belong to the Pan family in life

71
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,040
and in death.

72
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:21,990
I have no other intentions.

73
00:04:23,780 --> 00:04:25,700
If there's nothing else,
I shall take my leave.

74
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:28,100
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

75
00:04:28,100 --> 00:04:29,890
♪Blessed by fate♪

76
00:04:29,890 --> 00:04:35,050
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

77
00:04:35,050 --> 00:04:37,490
♪Your smiling face♪

78
00:04:37,490 --> 00:04:40,330
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

79
00:04:40,330 --> 00:04:43,950
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

80
00:04:44,470 --> 00:04:47,930
♪And wander the world together♪

81
00:04:47,930 --> 00:04:49,270
♪Holding you close♪

82
00:04:49,270 --> 00:04:51,810
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

83
00:04:51,810 --> 00:04:54,040
♪Your tenderness♪

84
00:04:54,070 --> 00:04:55,240
I have given you my heart.

85
00:04:57,070 --> 00:04:57,720
Did you know?

86
00:05:00,070 --> 00:05:00,870
What?

87
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:03,120
A year ago,

88
00:05:04,100 --> 00:05:06,590
with the glimpse on Zhuque Street
during the Lantern Festival,

89
00:05:07,950 --> 00:05:10,120
I thought I was just curious
about your background,

90
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,920
about how you could be so intelligent.

91
00:05:14,070 --> 00:05:14,720
But...

92
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:18,770
But when we met again,

93
00:05:18,780 --> 00:05:19,840
♪Though time slips by♪

94
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:20,700
♪As day turns into night♪

95
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,440
I realized it was much more than that.

96
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:25,540
♪I still remember our days
at Wangshi Tower♪

97
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:27,480
(What kind of strategy is this?)

98
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:30,800
But I am already

99
00:05:30,870 --> 00:05:32,070
married to another,

100
00:05:32,390 --> 00:05:34,480
and I deeply love my husband.

101
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:36,950
Your Highness's profound affection

102
00:05:39,430 --> 00:05:41,240
is something I cannot accept.

103
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:44,820
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

104
00:05:45,330 --> 00:05:48,560
♪And wander the world together♪

105
00:05:48,780 --> 00:05:50,030
♪Holding you close♪

106
00:05:50,030 --> 00:05:52,650
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

107
00:05:58,680 --> 00:05:59,480
Pan

108
00:06:01,630 --> 00:06:02,510
Yang.

109
00:06:07,430 --> 00:06:10,480
(Pan Residence)
Why was Yang sent to fight bandits?

110
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,430
My dear,

111
00:06:11,630 --> 00:06:12,950
we'll wait for your return.

112
00:06:13,430 --> 00:06:14,240
Good.

113
00:06:14,630 --> 00:06:15,430
Li Qingqing.

114
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:19,120
What do you want?

115
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:21,430
I am about to lead my troops out to war.

116
00:06:21,430 --> 00:06:23,430
As my first wife, instead of kneeling
at the door to see me off,

117
00:06:23,430 --> 00:06:24,600
you are in a hurry to go out.

118
00:06:24,830 --> 00:06:26,000
You have no manners at all!

119
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:27,830
What bad luck.

120
00:06:27,840 --> 00:06:29,460
I must have forgotten
to check the almanac today.

121
00:06:29,830 --> 00:06:31,560
Young Lady, I'm afraid the almanac

122
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:33,630
couldn't even fit a misfortune
as massive as this.

123
00:06:35,630 --> 00:06:39,160
Listen, the Crown Prince ordering me
to suppress the bandits

124
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:41,190
is an immense favor.

125
00:06:41,310 --> 00:06:43,480
Once I return in triumph,

126
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:46,830
a promotion to a higher rank
is just around the corner.

127
00:06:47,190 --> 00:06:48,070
When that time comes,

128
00:06:48,430 --> 00:06:50,240
I will be a Count.

129
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,040
Are you done?

130
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,190
You

131
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:59,430
are only worthy of watching Muyan
and me be deeply in love,

132
00:06:59,830 --> 00:07:03,120
and watching the Pan family
rise to glory under my leadership.

133
00:07:04,070 --> 00:07:04,920
You can only be

134
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,480
a despised and faded old wife

135
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,510
who lives like a widow
while still married.

136
00:07:07,510 --> 00:07:08,430
This is your destiny.

137
00:07:10,390 --> 00:07:12,430
I wish you a safe journey

138
00:07:12,430 --> 00:07:13,430
and an early victory.

139
00:07:13,830 --> 00:07:14,870
That's more like it.

140
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:16,630
When I return,

141
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,310
if I'm in a good mood,

142
00:07:18,510 --> 00:07:20,630
I might even
throw you a bone to gnaw on.

143
00:07:23,870 --> 00:07:24,560
Master...

144
00:07:25,510 --> 00:07:26,630
My dear,

145
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:28,390
you must take good care of yourself.

146
00:07:28,390 --> 00:07:29,000
Young Lady,

147
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,510
why did you even wish him success?

148
00:07:30,510 --> 00:07:33,390
A menace like him should just die
in the bandits' den and never come back.

149
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:36,510
I bet you that when he returns this time,

150
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,270
forget about becoming a Count,

151
00:07:38,310 --> 00:07:40,800
even his current title of Viscount
will be stripped away.

152
00:07:42,510 --> 00:07:43,800
How do you know, Young Lady?

153
00:07:44,270 --> 00:07:45,240
Haven't you noticed?

154
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:48,040
Every time the scheming fool
asks to meet me,

155
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:50,510
Pan Yang gets sent out
on some "crucial mission",

156
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:54,240
and then he comes back humiliated.

157
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,720
(He keeps tormenting
Pan Yang like this...)

158
00:07:56,830 --> 00:07:58,160
(Could he actually like me?)

159
00:07:58,510 --> 00:08:00,950
(Otherwise, this is a bit
too much commitment to the act.)

160
00:08:02,270 --> 00:08:04,870
(Sure enough, before Pan Yang
even reached Wangyang Ridge,)

161
00:08:04,870 --> 00:08:06,950
(his army was defeated,
and he was captured.)

162
00:08:10,630 --> 00:08:11,870
The bandits said

163
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:13,120
that within three days,

164
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:16,510
if we don't raise 50,000 taels
of ransom, they will kill Yang.

165
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:19,830
The imperial court
thinks Yang disgraced them

166
00:08:19,830 --> 00:08:21,000
and refuses to pay.

167
00:08:21,190 --> 00:08:23,120
What are we supposed to do?

168
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:26,000
(He is only tough at home.)

169
00:08:26,510 --> 00:08:29,950
Where can we find so much
silver upfront right now?

170
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:32,000
I told him long ago

171
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,480
that fighting bandits was dangerous,

172
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:35,440
but he just had to fight for the job.

173
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:37,200
Stop crying.

174
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,790
Now,

175
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:44,840
our only option is to mortgage

176
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,840
the Pan family ancestral home.

177
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:48,000
No!

178
00:08:49,630 --> 00:08:51,270
Selling it in a rush like this

179
00:08:51,390 --> 00:08:52,480
will mean a huge loss.

180
00:08:53,870 --> 00:08:54,840
Qingqing,

181
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:57,440
haven't you always been business-savvy

182
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:58,890
and accumulated quite a lot of savings?

183
00:08:59,510 --> 00:09:00,670
Qingqing,

184
00:09:00,910 --> 00:09:02,670
Yang is your husband.

185
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,320
As his first wife,

186
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:06,240
you can't just leave him to die.

187
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:09,440
Now you remember
that I am his first wife, huh?

188
00:09:10,750 --> 00:09:11,870
Things are already this way,

189
00:09:11,870 --> 00:09:13,390
and you are still
saying things like this.

190
00:09:13,630 --> 00:09:16,120
Are you going to just watch Yang die?

191
00:09:16,690 --> 00:09:18,600
When you were managing
the Li family businesses,

192
00:09:18,870 --> 00:09:20,120
you must have made a fortune.

193
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:22,990
You must have hidden away
a lot of personal savings, right?

194
00:09:26,870 --> 00:09:28,320
Your scheming tricks must be genetic.

195
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:30,910
Why don't you
bring out your hidden savings?

196
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:31,840
How...

197
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:34,030
How could I have any hidden savings?

198
00:09:36,270 --> 00:09:37,720
Looking at how you are dressed,

199
00:09:37,790 --> 00:09:39,750
you don't exactly seem short on cash.

200
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:41,360
The gold hairpin on your head,

201
00:09:41,670 --> 00:09:43,120
the jade bracelet on your wrist,

202
00:09:43,130 --> 00:09:44,570
and the fine silk you are wearing...

203
00:09:45,030 --> 00:09:47,150
Which of these isn't worth
a small fortune?

204
00:09:47,520 --> 00:09:49,360
Dressed in gold and silver,
yet playing poor.

205
00:09:49,630 --> 00:09:51,630
I bought all of these in the past.

206
00:09:51,630 --> 00:09:53,440
It doesn't matter when you bought them,

207
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:54,790
as long as they are valuable.

208
00:09:54,800 --> 00:09:56,670
Since you are so desperate
to save our husband,

209
00:09:56,670 --> 00:09:58,660
why don't you pawn all of these
for some quick cash?

210
00:09:58,670 --> 00:09:59,030
I...

211
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:01,270
Caiyuan, what are you standing there for?

212
00:10:01,630 --> 00:10:03,080
Help relieve her worries.

213
00:10:03,090 --> 00:10:04,200
What are you trying to do?

214
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:05,430
Saving someone is an emergency.

215
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:06,510
Don't touch me!

216
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:09,080
Don't you dodge.

217
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,030
- For the sake of your husband,
- Young Lady...

218
00:10:10,030 --> 00:10:11,630
what do these
worldly possessions matter?

219
00:10:11,630 --> 00:10:12,180
My hairpin...

220
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:12,790
Hand it over.

221
00:10:12,790 --> 00:10:13,720
My bracelet...

222
00:10:14,390 --> 00:10:15,240
This one...

223
00:10:15,510 --> 00:10:16,360
Don't...

224
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,300
There is another one over there.

225
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:19,840
Don't hide.

226
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:21,790
Give it here!

227
00:10:21,790 --> 00:10:22,200
Mine...

228
00:10:22,750 --> 00:10:24,000
There are so many.

229
00:10:39,390 --> 00:10:41,510
Looking at Li Muyan's
expression just now

230
00:10:41,630 --> 00:10:42,910
is satisfying.

231
00:10:43,630 --> 00:10:45,320
Keep these jewelry pieces safe.

232
00:10:45,670 --> 00:10:47,870
We will give them
to the beautiful lady in a while

233
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:50,480
as a token of respect from Li Muyan.

234
00:10:51,270 --> 00:10:53,630
Was this really done
by the Crown Prince?

235
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,150
Definitely.

236
00:10:55,210 --> 00:10:56,300
Quite satisfying, isn't it?

237
00:10:56,790 --> 00:10:58,910
Now I feel that Crown Prince
the scheming fool

238
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:01,240
isn't that annoying after all.

239
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,200
You scared me to death!

240
00:11:05,570 --> 00:11:06,360
Something happened.

241
00:11:13,980 --> 00:11:17,340
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

242
00:11:18,100 --> 00:11:21,500
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

243
00:11:22,260 --> 00:11:24,020
♪Your smile♪

244
00:11:24,260 --> 00:11:26,540
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

245
00:11:26,540 --> 00:11:30,220
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

246
00:11:30,700 --> 00:11:34,020
♪Yet I stand before you♪

247
00:11:34,740 --> 00:11:38,580
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

248
00:11:38,980 --> 00:11:40,900
♪Though fate tries♪

249
00:11:40,900 --> 00:11:43,500
♪To make us pass each other by♪

250
00:11:43,700 --> 00:11:47,140
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

251
00:11:47,380 --> 00:11:49,020
♪Though time slips by♪

252
00:11:49,020 --> 00:11:50,780
♪As day turns into night♪

253
00:11:51,300 --> 00:11:55,340
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

254
00:11:55,740 --> 00:11:58,140
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

255
00:11:58,140 --> 00:11:59,900
♪Blessed by fate♪

256
00:11:59,900 --> 00:12:05,060
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

257
00:12:05,060 --> 00:12:07,500
♪Your smiling face♪

258
00:12:07,500 --> 00:12:10,340
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

259
00:12:10,340 --> 00:12:13,980
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

260
00:12:14,500 --> 00:12:17,940
♪And wander the world together♪

261
00:12:17,940 --> 00:12:19,300
♪Holding you close♪

262
00:12:19,300 --> 00:12:21,820
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

263
00:12:21,820 --> 00:12:24,140
♪Your tenderness♪

264
00:12:24,140 --> 00:12:27,020
♪Is the brightest moon♪

265
00:12:27,020 --> 00:12:30,700
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

266
00:12:31,220 --> 00:12:34,540
♪Our love will never fade away♪

267
00:12:34,540 --> 00:12:36,980
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

268
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:41,780
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪

269
00:12:51,260 --> 00:12:53,420
♪Your smiling face♪

270
00:12:53,580 --> 00:12:56,180
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

271
00:12:56,500 --> 00:13:00,340
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

272
00:13:00,580 --> 00:13:04,060
♪And wander the world together♪

273
00:13:04,060 --> 00:13:05,380
♪Holding you close♪

274
00:13:05,380 --> 00:13:08,020
